webrtc peer to peer connection without signalling server.

signalling is done by copying offer and answer manually.

still need turn (or stun) server if connecting over internet.
seems to be no way to avoid that on the internet.
maybe possible to avoid on local network.

inspired by https://github.com/xem/miniWebRTC

which in turn was inspired by https://github.com/cjb/serverless-webrtc
